Name: Gravity Maze
About the game: Gravity Maze is a 2D physics maze game in which you can customize the maze and get balls to the end by changing gravity You can create custom size mazes that can be randomly generated or you can create your own maze. Challenge yourself by getting the balls to the end or just have physics fun. You can edit the maze or make creative designs with the maze editor. You can share your creation on the workshop.
